# Team Coding Conventions Template

This template helps you define team-specific coding standards for SAP CAP development. The agents will automatically reference these conventions when providing guidance.

## Getting Started

1. Copy this file to `prompts/team-conventions.md`
2. Fill in your team's specific conventions
3. The agents will automatically reference this file

---

