## Documentation Standards

### Code Comments
- **When to comment**: [Complex logic, business rules, other]
- **Comment style**: [JSDoc, inline, other]
- **Example**:
```javascript
/**
 * Validates order quantity against available stock
 * @param {Object} order - The order being validated
 * @returns {boolean} - True if valid, throws error otherwise
 */
function validateOrderQuantity(order) {
  // Implementation
}
```

### CDS Documentation
- **Required annotations**: [@title, @description]
- **Documentation level**: [Entity, field, service]
- **Example**:
```cds
@title: 'Books Catalog'
@description: 'Manages books available in the catalog'
entity Books {
  @title: 'Book Title'
  @description: 'The display title of the book'
  title : String(111);
}
```

### README Requirements
- **Project README sections**: [Setup, Usage, Deployment, other]
- **Service documentation**: [API docs, usage examples]

